snippet.title: ASSAULT SHELL Trailer
snippet.description: Fly in the hyper advanced Assault Shell, and fight against the horde of enemies using the powerful HYPER STAND and the extremely powerful BLANK STAND! End this accursed war once and for all, when ASSAULT SHELL releases on Gamejolt and Itch.io in 2020!
